    "section_wngWnF": {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": {
        "text_6jQgiE": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>The Founder's Letter</h3>",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "max_width": "normal",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "rte",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "text_YtNEUA": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>“ We’re still young, but we refuse to be boxed in. </p><p>I’ve never been one for a single label, and I’m guessing you aren’t either.</p><p>Before MOONLEE, I spent 15 years as a landscape architect. My life was—and still is—a chaotic blur: deep in a creative sprint one hour, presenting in a boardroom the next, and catching a flight by evening.</p><p>I love the feeling of being put-together, but I’ve always hated the tax we pay for it. The drive to the salon, the forced small talk, the rigid upkeep—it felt like just another chore on an endless to-do list. I wanted the salon look, but I refused to give up my Saturday morning for it.</p><p>MOONLEE was born from that exact frustration.</p><p>I took everything I knew about structural design and high-performance materials and scaled it down to your fingertips. The goal was simple: nails that look like they cost $100, but take exactly 5 minutes. Thin enough to type on a MacBook all day, yet strong enough to survive a gym session.</p><p>This isn't just about beauty. It’s about freedom. It’s the ability to switch roles effortlessly—from boss to bestie to traveler—without your routine slowing you down.</p><p>Let looking polished be the easiest thing you do today. You’ve got bigger things to design.</p><p>— <strong>Moon Lee, Founder & Designer</strong>”</p>",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "max_width": "none",
            "alignment": "left",
            "type_preset": "paragraph",
            "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
            "font_size": "1rem",
            "line_height": "normal",
            "letter_spacing": "normal",
            "case": "none",
            "wrap": "pretty",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
            "background": false,
            "background_color": "#00000026",
            "corner_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
